# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# KEY LEGEND - Shortened keys for token efficiency
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Structure Keys:
#
# Structure:
#   oapi         → openapi
#   inf          → info
#   srvs         → servers
#   comps        → components
#   sec          → security
#
# Info:
#   ttl          → title
#   ver          → version
#   desc         → description
#   sum          → summary
#
# Operations:
#   params       → parameters
#   body         → requestBody
#   resp         → responses
#   opId         → operationId
#   depr         → deprecated
#
# Parameters:
#   req          → required
#   sch          → schema
#   n            → name
#
# Schema:
#   props        → properties
#   itms         → items
#   t            → type
#   fmt          → format
#   def          → default
#   min          → minimum
#   max          → maximum
#   minL         → minLength
#   maxL         → maxLength
#   pat          → pattern
#   null         → nullable
#   all          → allOf
#   any          → anyOf
#   one          → oneOf
#   addProps     → additionalProperties
#
# Content:
#   cont         → content
#   json         → application/json
#   xml          → application/xml
#   form         → application/x-www-form-urlencoded
#   multipart    → multipart/form-data
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
